page.title: 10Biography-Faversham Child
page.content:
{A Day in the Life of Briony Dixon
On Saturday,the 20th. of July 1985 this was one day in my life. I got up and got dressed into my blue and green dress. Then I had my hair washed my Mum. After that I went down stairs to have my breakfast. My Dad has his breakfast before us because he goes to work. After breakfast I did some of my Maths. My Mum is 32,my Dad is 36. My Dad works at Gillets,an engineering firm,down the Creek. I am 8 years old and my sister,Esther,is 6. My best school activity is swimming in which I enjoy doing a handstand with legs straight over. My name is Briony Dixon.
{Briony Dixon
